Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mikagura Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.28,0:01:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Translation: Tamesuu & akutsu | Timing: PlasticYakuza | Editing: Collectr | Typeset & Encode: ShocWave | QC: Brush
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those were the good times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why did it have to turn out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Sensei ran off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Kanase-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Optimism's supposed to be your one redeeming\Nfeature, and here you are shedding tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's that about optimism being\Nmy only redeeming feature?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, straight from tears to anger\Nwith nothing in between!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we're all crossing the ocean to look for Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we shouldn't fight with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was my brother, the government official\Nin Manchuria, who sent me that letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the one saying that someone had seen\NDetective Mikagura Tokito there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you two are just tagging along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's tagging along?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to remind you that I paid for this trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If we fight among ourselves, it'll just\Ntake us longer to find Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiwa Shougo, who headed the League of the Bizarre,\Nand whom Sensei sent to jail, has escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...he'll try to get revenge on the\Nperson who imprisoned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. That's why we have to let Sensei\Nknow about it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She was on the ship with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't look like her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That girl's probably been sold to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.84,0:04:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see all of you. I'm sure you're tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, where's Tokito-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You really get to the point quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A chapel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where you saw Tokito-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I hurried to follow him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I lost him in the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you talk to the other people who were around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried, but everyone claimed ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must be hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I sent that letter to Shigeno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.72,0:05:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's our turn to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like some people have gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try talking to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a rare kind of visitor. Are you Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask why everyone's standing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They always let us use this place for our gatherings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But for some reason, it isn't open today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.36,0:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no one inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We wanted to talk to the person in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:05:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isude-san, the door won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How strange. Is it locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.72,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. We'd like to speak\Nto the person in charge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look around, so please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the famous Mikagura Detective Agency?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I'll gladly accept your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're short on people anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Morimatsu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make that decision by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not, Kawaba?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's worth it if they can help speed up the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it's going to be. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.80,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about the murder victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His name was Hatanaka Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a serious, earnest man who had a good\Nreputation with the people in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But judging by how brutally he was murdered,\Nhe must've been hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And Sensei might be involved in that secret as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you really be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be members of the\NMikagura Detective Agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but this place isn't like the Imperial capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Many places here are dangerous\Nfor unaccompanied girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we're actively searching,\Nwe might bump into Tokito-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotora?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying he was pressured to sell that land?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, by the man who runs the high-end\NJapanese restaurant called Kotora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His name is Nema Torazou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kotora. Nema Torazou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nema Torazou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm, back to what we were\Ntalking about a minute ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's true I asked him to sell\Nme his land, but I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you can't negotiate with a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,On a different note, all three of you\Nare too pretty to be detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:10:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially you. You're a lady from\Nsome rich family, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anything else to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That girl... I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Tomoe-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing. Let's catch up to Shigeno-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not getting wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have cute breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What about down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! No. Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That felt good, didn't it? And this will feel even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You see? You really feel it when\NI play with you down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg of you. Let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you admit you're feeling good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. Enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at how wet you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more than wet enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's ready for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's coming next will feel even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be getting used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls Seiichi brings me are always great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, serve him properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is quite a find.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotoshido, pay Seiichi the usual amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That nosy detective looking into\Nthe land finally disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and things were starting to go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But now we've got trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Before this gets out of hand, go to\Nthat woman you've been training,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and get the land rights from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I punish her enough, she'll do anything I ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kanase-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the shower. She's really taken a liking to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we should get some work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So where should we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.16,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema Torazou is the most suspicious at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a vulgar excuse for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'd murder someone\Nwithout a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we should jump to conclusions so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true he's the only one who seemed\Nto have a grudge against the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's actually someone else I find\Nsuspicious, but I don't know if it's related.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you discover something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.72,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman named Mimasaka Sue\Napparently went to the chapel often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She always picked times when no\None was around, like late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There were rumors she was\Nhaving an affair with the priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be! A priest devotes his life to God!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A man will always be a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you sure sound like you\Nknow what you're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,even though you have no experience to draw on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right back at you, Kumiyama-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-sama is the only one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you don't have any\Nromantic experience either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.44,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly is different?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.00,0:16:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop it, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, apparently someone who looked\Nlike Sensei stopped by the chapel before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Based on the description, I think it was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we hang around there, we'll be able to meet him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I was told, he used to visit the chapel often.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but nobody has seen him for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought we'd finally found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At least we know that he's somewhere nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure this case will lead us to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to find that woman named Mimasaka Sue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't decide whether she's a suspect or not
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,until we discover what her relationship\Nwith Hatanaka was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite a sight, Isuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it that good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.04,0:17:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already sopping wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're to bring me the property rights to this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I don't know much else about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.71,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.84,0:19:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, anything but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for rescuing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here and don't ever come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acquaintances of Detective-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know Tokito-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say I owe him my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.76,0:20:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come all the way from Japan to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that he used to\Nfrequent the chapel near here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but lately he hasn't been showing up there, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so you're looking for Mikagura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.95,0:21:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ryou Shakuryuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's my son Shinbu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we, the natives of this city, put our\Nfull effort into looking for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll find him right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate Japanese people, but that man is an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured that I'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we help them with the search?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many places that ladies like you can't enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to your hotel, and wait for us to contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They're taking too long!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to Shakuryuu-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that, Tomoe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We promised Shakuryuu-san that we'd wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.44,0:22:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe in them and wait a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We found Mikagura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.00,0:22:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell me he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.60,0:22:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to him might be worse than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.60,0:22:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.04,0:22:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.28,0:22:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.92,0:23:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,– Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,– Tokito-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.71,0:23:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.08,0:23:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you recognize us?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.40,0:23:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shigeno-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:24:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san, please take care of Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.20,0:24:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.12,0:24:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.56,0:24:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Use it however you like, for as long as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.36,0:24:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.56,0:24:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.12,0:24:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.95,0:24:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.40,0:24:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Opium...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.52,0:24:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't have any more opium!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.04,0:24:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.20,0:24:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Miwa...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.04,0:25:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.24,0:25:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Sensei... don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.00,0:26:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now. I'll accept everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.84,0:27:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.10,0:27:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.12,0:27:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I? What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.08,0:27:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.08,0:27:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.48,0:28:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-san, something horrible has happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.92,0:28:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Chizuru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.56,0:28:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nema Torazou has been murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.68,0:28:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and both of his arms were severed!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.72,0:29:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}anata ni todoke watashi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.72,0:29:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I send my heart to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kanashii yoru wa hitori namida ga ko to ko to ko
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.76,0:29:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On a sorrowful night, alone, my tears go drip, drop, drip, drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.72,0:29:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}anata ni todoke watashi no kokoro
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.72,0:29:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I send my heart to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.68,0:29:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}shizukana yoru ni hikaru tobira no oto oto oto oto
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.68,0:29:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,On a quiet night, the sound of a door –\Nthe sound, the sound, the sound, the sound!